# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CRITICAL: keep personal data and secrets out of git.
# The toolkit reads YOUR data from config/config.json and the files below.
# None of these should ever be committed. Only the *.example / *_TEMPLATE
# versions and the fictional examples/ folder are tracked.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Your real configuration (copy of config.example.json)
config/config.json

# Generated / personal data artifacts
model/*.xlsx
model/*.xls
dashboard/dashboard.html
dashboard/*.bak
market_intelligence.json
weekly_pulse_latest.json
weekly_pulse_history.jsonl
quarterly_input_Q*.json
quarterly_manifest.json
mc_trajectory.json
mc_summary.json
*_mc_summary.json
model/mc_summary.json

# Statements, tax docs, contracts, any source documents -- NEVER commit
Statements/
Taxes/
Contracts/
Backups/
documents/
*.pdf

# Secrets / credentials
*credentials*.json
*.env
.env
secrets.*

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
pylibs/
.venv/
venv/

# OS
.DS_Store
.~lock.*#
